# Cloudflare Pages — vivabellavista.com routing
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Trailing-slash normalisation for /c103
/c103   /c103/   301

# Serve c103 subfolder cleanly (splat pass-through)
/c103/*  /c103/:splat  200

# www → apex redirect (add www.vivabellavista.com as custom domain in CF Pages,
# then Cloudflare will handle the 301 automatically via bulk redirect — this is
# a fallback in case you need it at the Pages level)
# https://www.vivabellavista.com/*  https://vivabellavista.com/:splat  301
